          </tbody>
        </table>
        <p style="margin-top:18px;font-size:.85rem;color:var(--muted)">🏆 School achieved 100% pass rate in the UP Board Class 10 examinations. Results are displayed on the school notice board and reported to parents via PTM.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </section>
</div>

